				<li><a href="http://www.foodallergy.org/managing-food-allergies-at/dining-out/at-the-restaurant" title="http://www.foodallergy.org/managing-food-allergies-at/dining-out/at-the-restaurant" rel="external">At the Restaurant</a></li>
